hi, i am parisa, lighting and vis dev artist

you're a recruiter?

hi,

keep scrolling

2022 lighting and vis dev demo reel

https://youtu.be/-UjT1KDVkQ8

After graduation, I was having a hard time coming up with an idea for my demo reel, I didn't have a vision.

At the height of Covid, my last grandparent passed away and family decided to sell their old house, I couldn't be there in person.

Being thousands of kilometers away from them, I needed some sort of closure,

saying goodbye to a monumental chapter of my life.

"Hmm, this does sound like a vision to me"

I said,

784 hours later, I got myself a demo reel.

Closure? yeah, I got that one through meditation tho.

2020 graduation lighting demo reel

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jAO56ifHwSg

find my resume here

download

not a recruiter?

wanna look around?

item.title: About me
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
about me

A professionally trained Visual and CG Artist with a passion for tackling artistically and technically
challenging projects, who is looking to actualize skills in Lighting and Look Dev.
Works in a timely manner, while paying attention to details, as a result of experience in multiple disciplines.
Gained collaborative skills from teaching alongside volunteering for group college projects,
built up the confidence to start a career working within a studio system.
